msgid "The World Bank is one of the specialized agencies of the United Nations, which dealing with development. It has started its activities to assist in the reconstruction of Europe after the Second World War."
msgstr "البنـك الدولــيThe World Bank        هو احد الوكالات المتخصصة في الأمم المتحدة التي تعنى بالتنمية. وقد بدأ نشاطه بالمساعدة في اعمار اوربا بعد الحرب العالمية الثانية. للمزيد من المعلومات..."

#: Landing/view/landing/foreign-policy/international-organizations.phtml:62
msgid "UNESCO works, since its founding in (1945), to create the appropriate conditions for dialogue among civilization, cultures, and peoples, based upon respect for commonly shared values. Its headquarter is in Paris - France."
